data.description: Great opportunity for owner occupied or investor owned 2 family with a 3rd Floor In-Law studio apartment. 1st and 2nd floor units are currently rented under market rate. 1st Floor apartment boasts 2 bedrooms, full bath master bath, granite kitchen, hardwood floors throughout, 3/4 bath, washer & dryer hook ups in unit and central air. 2nd Floor apartment, 2 bedrooms, 1 full bath, wall to wall carpeting, eat in kitchen with washer dryer hook ups in unit, and tenant pays all the utilities. 3rd Floor offers an In-Law studio apartment with 1 bedroom, 1 full bath, eat in kitchenette, and an extra storage room. Level back yard with a deck to grill out and enjoy the weather. Driveway with off street parking for 3. Storage in extra closets in hallway & in the basement. Showings are only during open houses Fri 6/11. Sat 6/12 & Sun 6/13 from 3:30 - 6pm please make appointments via Showingtime.
